This is a web application to manage a stray cat association.
The application is hosted on a homelab server, its an Ubuntu server with a k3s cluster installed.
cert-manager is used to manage SSL certificates.
nginx is used as a reverse proxy to route traffic to the frontend and backend applications.
The tech stack includes:
- Frontend: Astro 5.5, Tailwind 3 (do not generate Tailwind 4 code, only version 3), React 18 and TypeScript.. 
- Backend: Strapi 5.11, url of the strapi application is https://dev.strapi.neitosden.fr